room_title: Escape room "The Cell" by Dare To Escape AZ in Phoenix
room_description:
You are an investigative journalist working for the renowned newspaper Daily Trumpet. A few weeks ago, an undercover FBI operative told a story about a terrorist organization, called Sons of Sahar, planning an attack on US soil.
After checking the story, you and your team agreed to meet with him in person at a diner in a remote town... When you arrived at the meeting location, however, men in black masks jumped the diner and subdued you. Now you must escape your imprisonment and recover the terrorist action plan on your way out.
